OL,3,CMan who stabbed ex-partner at her home
OL,4,Cpleads guilty to her murder
OL,6,FA man has admitted to murdering his ex-
OL,7,Fpartner who was fatally stabbed in her
OL,8,Fown home.
OL,10,FPerseverance Ncube, 35, known as
OL,11,F'Percy' to friends, was murdered by
OL,12,FObert Moyo.
OL,14,FMoyo had been due to go on trial at
OL,15,FManchester Crown Court but changed his
OL,16,Fplea to guilty on the first day of the
OL,17,Fcase.
