OL,6,FPolice were called to Dukesgate Grove
OL,7,Fin Little Hulton, Salford, to reports
OL,8,Fof a woman being found seriously hurt
OL,9,Fat 2:40am on Friday 10 November 2023.
OL,11,FNeighbours reported hearing
OL,12,F'screaming' and went to help her. But
OL,13,FMs Ncube was later pronounced dead.
OL,15,FMoyo, 46, of Pennington Road, Bolton,
OL,16,Fwas arrested and charged.
OL,18,FHe now faces a life sentence, and is
OL,19,Fdue to appear in court again on 30
OL,20,FApril for his sentencing hearing.
