OL,3,CMan who stabbed ex-partner at her home
OL,4,Cpleads guilty to her murder
OL,6,FMs Ncube's family told of their
OL,7,F"immense pain" following her death.
OL,9,FShe was described as being "loving and
OL,10,Fdevoted" and an "active member of her
OL,11,Fchurch". They said that she had been
OL,12,F"cruelly taken from us due to domestic
OL,13,Fviolence".
OL,15,F"Percy had just celebrated her 35th
OL,16,Fbirthday in October, and her passing
OL,17,Fhas left us with an immeasurable sense
OL,18,Fof loss," the statement continued.
