OL,6,FA candlelit vigil was held on the
OL,7,Fstreet outside her home the day after
OL,8,Fher death. Residents lit candles and
OL,9,Flaid them in the shape of hearts and
OL,10,Fthe letter 'P'.
OL,12,FFriends from Ms Ncube's church spoke
OL,13,Fof her 'true soul' and 'peaceful'
OL,14,Fnature.
OL,16,F"We literally had a real angel living
OL,17,Fwith us," one said.
OL,19,F"Words can't express how good this
OL,20,Fwoman was. Nothing I say can explain
OL,21,Fhow good she was as a person."
