OL,6,FAnother person who attended the vigil
OL,7,Fsaid: "You just don't think something
OL,8,Flike this will happen on your
OL,9,Fdoorstep. We're a really tight knit
OL,10,Fcommunity. We just wanted to do
OL,11,Fsomething to bring people together."
